,"Properties.Property_Master_Attack Speed_Name":"攻击速度","Properties.Property_Master_Attack Speed_AltText":"提高你每秒可进行的攻击次数。","Properties.Property_Master_Cast Speed_Name":"施法速度","Properties.Property_Master_Cast Speed_AltText":"提高你每秒可施放的法术数量。","Properties.Property_Master_Critical Strike Chance_Name":"暴击几率","Properties.Property_Master_Critical Strike Chance_AltText":"提高你造成暴击的几率。你的基础暴击几率默认为5%, 因此在无其他修正值的情况下, 提高100%暴击几率会使你的暴击几率变为10%。","Properties.Property_Master_Critical Strike Multiplier_Name":"暴击伤害加成","Properties.Property_Master_Critical Strike Multiplier_AltText":"提高你的暴击造成的伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken_Name":"承受伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken_AltText":"修正你承受的伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Health_Name":"生命","Properties.Property_Master_Health_AltText":"提高你的最大生命","Properties.Property_Master_Mana_Name":"魔力","Properties.Property_Master_Mana_AltText":"提高你的最大魔力","Properties.Property_Master_Movement Speed_Name":"移动速度","Properties.Property_Master_Movement Speed_AltText":"提高你的移动速度","Properties.Property_Master_Armor_Name":"护甲","Properties.Property_Master_Armor_AltText":"护甲会减少总体承受的伤害, 但对持续伤害无效。对物理伤害尤为有效。","Properties.Property_Master_Dodge Rating_Name":"躲避值","Properties.Property_Master_Dodge Rating_AltText":"提高躲避几率","Properties.Property_Master_Stun Avoidance_Name":"晕眩避免","Properties.Property_Master_Stun Avoidance_AltText":"所有攻击都有几率基于伤害对你施加晕眩。晕眩避免可降低此几率。","Properties.Property_Master_Fire Resistance_Name":"火焰抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Fire Resistance_AltText":"降低你承受的火焰伤害, 上限为75%。","Properties.Property_Master_Cold Resistance_Name":"冰霜抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Cold Resistance_AltText":"降低你承受的冰霜伤害, 上限为75%。","Properties.Property_Master_Lightning Resistance_Name":"闪电抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Lightning Resistance_AltText":"降低你承受的闪电伤害, 上限为75%。","Properties.Property_Master_Ward Retention_Name":"能量护盾维持","Properties.Property_Master_Ward Retention_AltText":"能量护盾是一种临时护盾, 没有上限, 且会持续衰减。能量护盾维持可以减缓这种衰减。","Properties.Property_Master_Health Regen_Name":"生命再生","Properties.Property_Master_Health Regen_AltText":"提高你的生命持续再生的速率","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Regen_Name":"魔力再生","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Regen_AltText":"提高你的魔力持续再生的速率","Properties.Property_Master_Strength_Name":"力量","Properties.Property_Master_Strength_AltText":"每点力量会提高4%护甲, 并使依赖你和伙伴力量的技能得到增强。","Properties.Property_Master_Vitality_Name":"活力","Properties.Property_Master_Vitality_AltText":"每点活力会提供6点生命, 以及1%毒素抗性和腐化抗性。","Properties.Property_Master_Intelligence_Name":"智力","Properties.Property_Master_Intelligence_AltText":"每点智力会提供2%能量护盾维持, 并使依赖精心研究的魔法的技能得到增强。","Properties.Property_Master_Dexterity_Name":"敏捷","Properties.Property_Master_Dexterity_AltText":"每点敏捷会增加4点躲避值, 并使依赖熟练操作武器的技能得到增强。","Properties.Property_Master_Attunement_Name":"协调","Properties.Property_Master_Attunement_AltText":"每点协调会提供2点魔力, 并使依赖于你体内和周围环境中与生俱来的魔法的技能得到增强。","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Dealt to Mana Before Health_Name":"伤害由魔力优先承受而非生命","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Dealt to Mana Before Health_AltText":"你承受伤害的一部分转为消耗魔力而非生命。每点魔力等同于5点生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Channel Cost_Name":"引导消耗","Properties.Property_Master_Channel Cost_AltText":"修正引导技能每秒魔力消耗","Properties.Property_Master_Void Resistance_Name":"虚空抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Void Resistance_AltText":"降低你承受的虚空伤害, 上限为75%。","Properties.Property_Master_Necrotic Resistance_Name":"腐化抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Necrotic Resistance_AltText":"降低你承受的腐化伤害, 上限为75%。","Properties.Property_Master_Poison Resistance_Name":"毒素抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Poison Resistance_AltText":"降低你承受的毒素伤害, 上限为75%。","Properties.Property_Master_Block Chance_Name":"格挡几率","Properties.Property_Master_Block Chance_AltText":"增加至你的格挡几率。被格挡的攻击伤害总降, 具体取决于你的格挡效率。","Properties.Property_Master_All Resistances_Name":"所有抗性","Properties.Property_Master_All Resistances_AltText":"增加至你的物理、火焰、冰霜、闪电、腐化、虚空与毒素抗性。","Properties.Property_Master_Health Gain_Name":"恢复生命","Properties.Property_Master_Health Gain_AltText":"立即恢复生命","Properties.Property_Master_Ward Gain_Name":"获得能量护盾","Properties.Property_Master_Ward Gain_AltText":"立即获得能量护盾。能量护盾是一种临时护盾, 且基于你当前的护盾量衰减。","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Gain_Name":"恢复魔力","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Gain_AltText":"立即恢复魔力","Properties.Property_Master_Adaptive Spell Damage_Name":"自适应法术伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Adaptive Spell Damage_AltText":"增加伤害至所有法术。增加伤害类型与法术对应基础伤害相同。","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Ailment Duration_Name":"提高异常状态持续时间","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Ailment Duration_AltText":"提高你造成的异常状态的持续时间","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Ailment Effect_Name":"提高异常状态效果","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Ailment Effect_AltText":"提高你造成的异常状态的效果","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Healing Effectiveness_Name":"提高治疗效率","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Healing Effectiveness_AltText":"提高治疗技能的生命恢复量","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Stun Chance_Name":"提高晕眩几率","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Stun Chance_AltText":"所有能造成足够伤害的击中都有几率造成晕眩。提高晕眩几率可以提高此几率。","Properties.Property_Master_All Attributes_Name":"所有属性","Properties.Property_Master_All Attributes_AltText":"增加至你的力量、敏捷、智力、协调与活力。","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Chance To Find Potions_Name":"提高发现药剂几率","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Chance To Find Potions_AltText":"提高你发现药剂的几率。药剂显示在生命球旁边, 消耗药剂（默认按1键）可恢复生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Health Gained on Potion Use_Name":"生命恢复于使用药剂时","Properties.Property_Master_Health Gained on Potion Use_AltText":"药剂显示在生命球旁边, 消耗药剂（默认按1键）可恢复生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Potion Slots_Name":"药剂栏位","Properties.Property_Master_Potion Slots_AltText":"增加至你的药剂上限。药剂显示在生命球旁边, 消耗药剂（默认按1键）可恢复生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Leeched as Health_Name":"伤害转化为生命偷取","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Leeched as Health_AltText":"你造成伤害的一部分将在三秒内持续为你恢复生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Elemental Resistance_Name":"元素抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Elemental Resistance_AltText":"增加至你的火焰、冰霜与闪电抗性。","Properties.Property_Master_Block Effectiveness_Name":"格挡效率","Properties.Property_Master_Block Effectiveness_AltText":"格挡效率减轻你格挡时承受的攻击伤害。","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Stun Immunity Duration_Name":"提高晕眩免疫持续时间","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Stun Immunity Duration_AltText":"晕眩结束后, 你默认在1秒内免疫晕眩。此效果会提高免疫效果的持续时间。","Properties.Property_Master_Stun Immunity_Name":"晕眩免疫","Properties.Property_Master_Stun Immunity_AltText":"防止你被晕眩","Properties.Property_Master_Dark Protection (deprecated)_Name":"黑暗防护（过时）","Properties.Property_Master_Dark Protection (deprecated)_AltText":"抵抗虚空、腐化与毒素伤害。10点黑暗防护相当于10点只对虚空、毒素或腐化伤害生效的生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Penetration_Name":"抗性穿透","Properties.Property_Master_Penetration_AltText":"抗性穿透可使抗性低于0%, 对无抗性的敌人也可提高伤害。此效果适用于所有伤害, 包括持续伤害。","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to receive a Glancing Blow when hit_Name":"几率触发伤害偏斜于被击中时","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to receive a Glancing Blow when hit_AltText":"被击中时触发伤害偏斜的几率。伤害偏斜使承受伤害总降35%。","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Cost_Name":"魔力消耗","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Cost_AltText":"修正你施放技能的消耗","Properties.Property_Master_Freeze Rate Multiplier_Name":"冻结率加成","Properties.Property_Master_Freeze Rate Multiplier_AltText":"冰霜技能击中时有几率冻结目标, 冻结几率等于其冻结率除以目标的生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Efficiency_Name":"魔力效率","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Efficiency_AltText":"提高你的魔力使用效率。\n魔力消耗 = 基础魔力消耗 / (1 + 魔力效率)","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Cooldown Recovery Speed_Name":"提高冷却恢复速度","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Cooldown Recovery Speed_AltText":"提高你的技能冷却速度","Properties.Property_Master_Physical Resistance_Name":"物理抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Physical Resistance_AltText":"降低你承受的物理伤害, 上限为75%。","Properties.Property_Master_Current Health Drained per Second_Name":"每秒流失当前生命","Properties.Property_Master_Current Health Drained per Second_AltText":"每秒流失你当前生命的一定百分比。此效果不会致死。","Properties.Property_Master_Cull on Hit_Name":"终结于击中时","Properties.Property_Master_Cull on Hit_AltText":"敌人生命降至此百分比时会被击杀","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Lightning_Name":"承受的伤害转化为闪电伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Lightning_AltText":"减免前的伤害转化为闪电伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Physical_Name":"承受的伤害转化为物理伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Physical_AltText":"减免前的伤害转化为物理伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Fire_Name":"承受的伤害转化为火焰伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Fire_AltText":"减免前的伤害转化为火焰伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Cold_Name":"承受的伤害转化为冰霜伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Cold_AltText":"减免前的伤害转化为冰霜伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Void_Name":"承受的伤害转化为虚空伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Void_AltText":"减免前的伤害转化为虚空伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Poison_Name":"承受的伤害转化为毒素伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Poison_AltText":"减免前的伤害转化为毒素伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Necrotic_Name":"承受的伤害转化为腐化伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken as Necrotic_AltText":"减免前的伤害转化为腐化伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Maximum Companions_Name":"伙伴上限","Properties.Property_Master_Maximum Companions_AltText":"提高野蛮人可召唤的伙伴上限","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to gain Haste for 1 second on Hit_Name":"几率获得持续1秒的急速于击中时","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to gain Haste for 1 second on Hit_AltText":"急速是增益状态, 可提高30%移动速度。无法叠加。","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Chill Attackers_Name":"冰缓攻击者几率","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Chill Attackers_AltText":"击中你的敌人有几率被冰缓。每层冰缓会降低12%攻击、施法与移动速度（与其他修正值相乘算）, 持续4秒。可叠加3层, 对玩家效果总降50%。","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Slow Attackers_Name":"迟缓攻击者几率","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Slow Attackers_AltText":"击中你的敌人有几率被迟缓。每层迟缓降低20%移动速度（与其他修正值相乘算）, 持续4秒。可叠加3层, 对玩家效果总降50%。","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Reflected to Attackers_Name":"伤害反射至攻击者","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Reflected to Attackers_AltText":"你受到攻击时, 直接对攻击者造成伤害, 且不受敌人的防御属性影响。","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Reflected_Name":"伤害反射","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Reflected_AltText":"承受的伤害会有一部分反射给攻击者。减免机制会在反射之前计算。伤害反射不影响你承受的伤害总量。","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Shock Attackers_Name":"感电攻击者几率","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Shock Attackers_AltText":"击中你的敌人有几率被感电。感电降低5%闪电抗性, 提高20%被晕眩几率, 持续4秒, 至多叠加10层。对首领与玩家降低60%效果。","Properties.Property_Master_Critical Strike Avoidance_Name":"暴击避免","Properties.Property_Master_Critical Strike Avoidance_AltText":"有几率使敌人对你造成的暴击降为普通攻击。敌人默认有5%暴击几率。","Properties.Property_Master_Potion Health Converted to Ward_Name":"药剂恢复生命转化为能量护盾","Properties.Property_Master_Potion Health Converted to Ward_AltText":"使用药剂恢复生命的一部分转化为能量护盾。高于100%的部分无效。","Properties.Property_Master_Ward Gained on Potion Use_Name":"能量护盾获得于使用药剂时","Properties.Property_Master_Ward Gained on Potion Use_AltText":"能量护盾是一种临时护盾, 可以保护你的生命, 但会持续衰减。","Properties.Property_Master_Overkill Damage Leeched as Health_Name":"溢出伤害转化为生命偷取","Properties.Property_Master_Overkill Damage Leeched as Health_AltText":"你击败一名敌人时, 溢出伤害的一部分将在三秒内持续为你恢复生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Ward per Second_Name":"每秒获得能量护盾","Properties.Property_Master_Ward per Second_AltText":"使你随时间获得能量护盾。能量护盾会持续衰减, 所以你的能量护盾恢复值与衰减值相等时, 你的能量护盾值会达到稳定。","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Dealt to Mana Before Health or Ward_Name":"伤害由魔力优先承受而非生命或能量护盾","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Dealt to Mana Before Health or Ward_AltText":"你承受伤害的一部分转为消耗魔力而非生命或能量护盾。每点魔力等同于5点生命。","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Stun Duration_Name":"提高晕眩持续时间","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Stun Duration_AltText":"提高你造成的晕眩的持续时间","Properties.Property_Master_Duration of Stuns Received_Name":"被晕眩的持续时间","Properties.Property_Master_Duration of Stuns Received_AltText":"降低晕眩时间","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Gain 30 Ward when Hit_Name":"被击中时获得30点能量护盾几率","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Gain 30 Ward when Hit_AltText":"能量护盾是一种临时护盾, 可以保护你的生命, 且会持续衰减。超过100%部分的几率不起作用。承受伤害后生效, 但对致死伤害无效。","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Spent Gained as Ward_Name":"魔力消耗转化为能量护盾","Properties.Property_Master_Mana Spent Gained as Ward_AltText":"能量护盾是一种临时护盾, 可以保护你的生命, 但会持续衰减。只影响消耗的魔力, 不影响流失的魔力。","Properties.Property_Master_Ailment Conversion_Name":"异常状态转化","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Leech Rate_Name":"提高偷取速率","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Leech Rate_AltText":"提高生命偷取恢复生命的速度。此效果不影响偷取的生命总量。","Properties.Property_Master_Freeze Rate per stack of Chill_Name":"每层冰缓冻结率","Properties.Property_Master_Freeze Rate per stack of Chill_AltText":"提高每层冰缓效果提供的冻结率（与其他修正值相乘算）","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Drop Rate_Name":"提高掉落几率","Properties.Property_Master_Increased Experience_Name":"提高经验","Properties.Property_Master_Physical and Void Resistance_Name":"物理与虚空抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Physical and Void Resistance_AltText":"增加至你的物理与虚空抗性。","Properties.Property_Master_Necrotic and Poison Resistance_Name":"腐化与毒素抗性","Properties.Property_Master_Necrotic and Poison Resistance_AltText":"增加至你的腐化与毒素抗性。","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken From Nearby Enemies_Name":"承受附近敌人伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Block Chance Against Distant Enemies_Name":"对远处敌人格挡几率","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Receive a Critical Strike_Name":"承受暴击几率","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Receive a Critical Strike_AltText":"增加你承受攻击时被暴击的几率。不受攻击者的提高暴击几率加成。","Properties.Property_Master_Endurance_Name":"耐伤","Properties.Property_Master_Endurance_AltText":"你的生命低于耐伤阈值时, 耐伤会降低你承受的伤害。上限为60%。","Properties.Property_Master_Endurance Threshold_Name":"耐伤阈值","Properties.Property_Master_Endurance Threshold_AltText":"你的生命低于耐伤阈值时, 耐伤会降低你承受的伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Level of Skills_Name":"技能等级","Properties.Property_Master_Damage Taken While Moving_Name":"移动时承受伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Maximum Health gained as Endurance Threshold_Name":"基于最大生命提高耐伤阈值","Properties.Property_Master_Maximum Health gained as Endurance Threshold_AltText":"获得相当于你最大生命一部分的耐伤阈值。生命低于耐伤阈值时, 耐伤会降低你承受的伤害。","Properties.Property_Master_reduced Bonus Damage Taken from Critical Strikes_Name":"降低承受暴击额外伤害","Properties.Property_Master_reduced Bonus Damage Taken from Critical Strikes_AltText":"降低暴击造成的额外伤害。无法使伤害低于非暴击。此属性与其它伤害修正值相乘算, 但多个来源的此属性之间相加。","Properties.Property_Master_More Damage Per Stack_Name":"伤害总增自每层","Properties.Property_Master_More Damage Per Stack_AltText":"计算目标身上的层数。与其他修正值相乘算。","Properties.Property_Master_increased Area for Area Skills_Name":"提高范围技能的范围","Properties.Property_Master_increased Area for Area Skills_AltText":"提高带有范围标签的技能范围。与其他来源的提高范围属性相加。","Properties.Property_Master_Global Conditional Damage_Name":"全域条件伤害","Properties.Property_Master_Global Conditional Damage_AltText":"与其他修正值相乘算","Properties.Property_Master_Armor Mitigation also applies to Damage over Time_Name":"护甲减伤效果也对持续伤害生效","Properties.Property_Master_Armor Mitigation also applies to Damage over Time_AltText":"例如, 若你有足够的护甲使承受的击中伤害降低60%, 且你的50%护甲减伤对持续伤害生效, 则护甲将使你承受的持续伤害降低30%。","Properties.Property_Master_Ward Decay Threshold_Name":"护盾衰减阈值","Properties.Property_Master_Ward Decay Threshold_AltText":"低于能量护盾衰减阈值时, 能量护盾不再衰减。低于衰减阈值的能量护盾部分不会计算在衰减速率公式中。例如, 你的能量护盾衰减阈值为500, 所以能量护盾不会衰减至低于500, 而且当能量护盾数值为1000时, 衰减速率是默认数值的一半。","Properties.Property_Master_Parry Chance_Name":"招架几率","Properties.Property_Master_Parry Chance_AltText":"招架一次攻击会使承受的伤害变为零, 但不会防止该次攻击的其他效果。招架几率对持续伤害不生效, 且上限为75%。被招架的攻击无法同时被格挡或触发伤害偏斜。","Properties.Property_Master_Lens_Name":"镜片","Properties.Property_Master_Lens_AltText":"提高特定预言在观星台中出现的几率。\n\n屏蔽特定类型活动或提高预言消耗的镜片无法叠加。","Properties.Property_Master_Tracker Property_Name":"追踪者属性","Properties.Property_Master_Unimportance Modifier_Name":"不重要的修正值","Properties.Property_Master_Immunity_Name":"免疫","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Cast When Hit_Name":"几率施放于被击中时","Properties.Property_Master_Chance to Cast When Hit_AltText":"若该技能有冷却时间, 则其必须在技能栏内且未处于冷却才可触发此效果, 且触发后将进入冷却。","Properties.null_Name":"Error Idol Altar Property Not Found","Properties.null_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_0_Name":"预兆神像上限","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_0_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_1_Name":"折射栏位神像前缀与后缀效果","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_1_AltText":"若神像的任意部分在折射栏位内, 则视为其处于该栏位内","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_2_Name":"折射栏位神像前缀效果","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_2_AltText":"若神像的任意部分在折射栏位内, 则视为其处于该栏位内","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_3_Name":"折射栏位神像后缀效果","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_3_AltText":"若神像的任意部分在折射栏位内, 则视为其处于该栏位内","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_4_Name":"折射栏位神像编织者附魔词缀效果","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_4_AltText":"若神像的任意部分在折射栏位内, 则视为其处于该栏位内","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_5_Name":"编织者神像装备上限","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_5_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_6_Name":"异端神像装备上限","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_6_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_7_Name":"精装神像装备上限","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_7_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_8_Name":"腐化神像装备上限","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_8_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_9_Name":"躲避值自装备的每个腐化神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_9_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_10_Name":"魔力自装备的每个腐化神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_10_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_11_Name":"护甲自装备的每个腐化神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_11_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_12_Name":"能量护盾衰减阈值自装备的每个腐化神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_12_AltText":"低于能量护盾衰减阈值时, 能量护盾不再衰减。低于衰减阈值的能量护盾部分不会计算在衰减速率公式中。例如, 你的能量护盾衰减阈值为500, 所以能量护盾不会衰减至低于500, 而且当能量护盾数值为1000时, 衰减速率是默认数值的一半。","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_13_Name":"生命自装备的每个预兆神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_13_AltText":"异端神像是受到编织者的触摸附魔的神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_14_Name":"每秒获得能量护盾自装备的每个异端神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_14_AltText":"异端神像是受到编织者的触摸附魔的神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_15_Name":"降低承受暴击额外伤害自装备的每个异端神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_15_AltText":"降低暴击造成的额外伤害。无法使伤害低于非暴击。此属性与其它伤害修正值相乘算, 但多个来源的此属性之间相加。异端神像是受到编织者的触摸附魔的神像。","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_16_Name":"提高魔力再生自装备的每个华丽神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_16_AltText":"null","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_17_Name":"提高生命自装备的每个巨型神像","Properties.Property_IdolAltar_17_AltText":"null","Properties.Prop