al Queen":"德拉尔女王","Actors.Actor_Name_Fateweaver Lachesis":"命运编织者拉克西丝","Actors.Actor_Name_Fateweaver Clotho":"命运编织者克洛托","Actors.Actor_Name_Fateweaver Atropos":"命运编织者阿特洛波斯","Actors.Actor_Name_Seeker of the Shards":"碎片追寻者","Actors.Actor_Name_Woven Firstborn":"初生编织","Actors.Actor_Name_Tomb Guardian":"墓穴卫士","Actors.Actor_Name_Omen of Solitude":"独行预兆","Actors.Actor_Name_Omen of Strife":"纷争预兆","Actors.Actor_Name_Omen of Havoc":"浩劫预兆","Actors.Actor_Name_Omen of Silence":"沉默预兆","Actors.Actor_Name_Vision of the Observer":"观察者的幻象","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_None":"消逝秘境","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_None":"","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_ManyRunePrisons":"流放位面","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_ManyRunePrisons":"包含许多符文监牢","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_ManyShrines":"虚假神殿","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_ManyShrines":"一座来自被遗忘的时间线的神庙, 里面摆满了神龛。","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_ManyCaches":"未知藏宝地","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_ManyCaches":"在这个满是沉船残骸的墓地中, 遗失的宝藏随处可见。","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_NemesisTower":"征服高塔","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_NemesisTower":"直面多个复仇武装以攀登高塔。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_NemesisTower_0":"击败或放逐每层的复仇武装以攀登高塔","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_NemesisTower_1":"登上塔顶并摧毁复仇化身","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_EndgameMajasa":"神躯墓穴","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_EndgameMajasa":"在她贪婪收集来的宝库中直面玛加莎。平息她的怒火, 夺取她的财富。\n\n必定掉落1件暗金饰品。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_EndgameMajasa_0":"击杀玛加莎","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_WeaverAltar":"编织者之塔","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_WeaverAltar":"编织者之塔的顶端有一座编织者祭坛","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_BossRush":"纷争护手","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_BossRush":"与一系列被强化的首领及勇士敌人进行战斗。\n\n\n最后一个敌人倒下时, 将掉落两件相同的随机暗金物品, 同时你将获得通往祭坛的权限。在这里, 你可以献祭一件暗金物品, 以重掷另一件相同暗金物品的属性。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_BossRush_0":"击杀全部7名首领及其勇士","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_BossRush_1":"每次击败首领会生成1名新勇士","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_BossRush_2":"进入祭坛","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_ArenaChampions":"勇士竞技场","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_ArenaChampions":"竞技场冠军之间的混战。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ArenaChampions_0":"击败全部3名竞技场冠军","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_ChampionRush":"骷髅之柱","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_ChampionRush":"骷髅之柱高高耸立在魂火堡垒之上。巫妖克里莫斯正是在这里用灵魂余烬复活了过去和未来时代的勇士。站在柱顶, 击败所有敢于反抗你的勇士。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ChampionRush_0":"击杀全部9名勇士","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_EndgameOrian":"追寻者之峰","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_EndgameOrian":"在战争营地的顶峰击杀占卜师奥利安, 碎片追寻者。\n\n必定掉落1件暗金近战武器。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_EndgameOrian_0":"击杀占卜师奥利安","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_SoulGamblerTimeTrial":"灵魂铸厂","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_SoulGamblerTimeTrial":"在时间耗尽前击杀尽可能多的敌人以收集灵魂余烬, 随后可在灵魂赌徒处消耗灵魂余烬。\n\n购买的第一件物品必定为暗金物品。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_SoulGamblerTimeTrial_0":"收集灵魂余烬","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_SoulGamblerTimeTrial_1":"额外稳定值奖励会随时间增长。达到满值后, 你将被传送。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_SoulGamblerTimeTrial_2":"在灵魂赌徒处花费灵魂余烬。第一次购买的物品必定为暗金物品。","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_ChonkerDrake":"对极裂隙","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_ChonkerDrake":"前往远古纪元, 消灭制造对极裂隙的存在。\n\n必定掉落1件暗金防具。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ChonkerDrake_0":"击杀对极龙","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_EndgameDraalQueen":"虫巢之心","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_EndgameDraalQueen":"消灭落石山脉地下深处的德拉尔女王。\n\n必定掉落1件暗金远程或施法武器。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_EndgameDraalQueen_0":"击杀德拉尔女王","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_WeaverSpreader":"迷林回廊","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_WeaverSpreader":"击杀游荡在小径与编织大厅中的命运编织者, 将编织者的信徒们驱散到周围的秘境中。\n\n在这些秘境中, 编织者的信徒群体更为强大, 但也会掉落大量记忆琥珀。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_WeaverSpreader_0":"击杀全部3名命运编织者","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_WeaverSpreader_1":"击杀全部3名命运编织者（1/3）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_WeaverSpreader_2":"击杀全部3名命运编织者（2/3）","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_SetCraftingBridge":"雄伟大桥","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_SetCraftingBridge":"突破雄伟大桥沿线的防御工事, 前往命运熔炉, 即可分解套装物品并重铸。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_SetCraftingBridge_0":"突破防御工事","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_SetCraftingBridge_1":"击杀守卫命运熔炉的鹰首人","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_SetCraftingBridge_2":"使用命运熔炉分解套装物品","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_ZombiesVsPlants":"蔓生墓园","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_ZombiesVsPlants":"帮助墓园的居民击退入侵的植物。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ZombiesVsPlants_0":"击退入侵植物","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ZombiesVsPlants_1":"消灭东北方的向日葵","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ZombiesVsPlants_2":"消灭东方的向日葵","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ZombiesVsPlants_3":"消灭南方的向日葵","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ZombiesVsPlants_4":"消灭西方的向日葵","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ZombiesVsPlants_5":"消灭西北方的向日葵","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ZombiesVsPlants_6":"消灭所有入侵蔓花","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_ShadeGauntlet":"毁灭之源","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_ShadeGauntlet":"击败每种类型的奥罗比斯之影, 以重置此时间线的秘境之网, 并根据与此角色使用相同仓库的最高腐败值角色获得腐败值。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ShadeGauntlet_0":"激活腐化时间线之门","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_ShadeGauntlet_1":"击杀5名奥罗比斯之影","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_UberAterroth":"永恒门扉","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_UberAterroth":"阿波罗斯在门后等着你。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_UberAterroth_0":"击败阿波罗斯","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_Baroness":"失落要塞","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_Baroness":"穿过血染大厅, 直面男爵夫人。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_Baroness_0":"找到并击杀男爵夫人","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_Brewery":"大酒坊","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_Brewery":"在酿酒厂里畅饮啤酒并大打出手, 取得胜利后赢取酿酒大师的皮带扣。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_Brewery_0":"击败酿造者","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_Turtle":"远视乌龟","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_Turtle":"保护正在运送变形宝石的巨大乌龟。\n\n击败攻击者后, 你可以利用宝石的力量重新编织具有传奇潜能的暗金物品的命运, 增加或减少它们的传奇潜能。新的传奇潜能的生成方式与该类型新掉落的暗金物品的传奇潜能生成方式相同。因此, 对于大多数暗金物品来说, 传奇潜能最有可能变为0。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_Turtle_0":"获取变形宝石","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_Turtle_1":"击退拉贡的军队","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_Turtle_2":"使用变形宝石","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_WovenVesselOfChaos":"编织混沌容器","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_WovenVesselOfChaos":"摧毁此秘境中的混沌容器, 以重掷附近未完成秘境的奖励。","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_WovenVesselOfMemory":"编织记忆容器","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_WovenVesselOfMemory":"摧毁此秘境中的记忆容器, 以复原附近的已完成秘境, 你可以再次完成这些秘境并获得奖励。\n\n编织秘境或包含有记忆容器、混沌容器的秘境不受影响。","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_RunePrisonComplex":"符文监牢设施","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_RunePrisonComplex":"一座符文大师的堡垒, 来自符文监牢的错位时空, 其创造的奥术实验也被封印其中。\n\n击败符文看守, 以解除围绕奇术装置的屏障, 并制作你自己的实验物品。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_0":"打开符文监牢以引诱出符文看守（0/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_1":"击杀符文看守（0/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_2":"打开符文监牢以引诱出符文看守（1/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_3":"击杀符文看守（1/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_4":"打开符文监牢以引诱出符文看守（2/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_5":"击杀符文看守（2/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_6":"打开符文监牢以引诱出符文看守（3/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_7":"击杀符文看守（3/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_8":"打开符文监牢以引诱出符文看守（4/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_9":"击杀符文看守（4/5）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_RunePrisonComplex_10":"返回奇术装置处","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_TimeTravelArena":"欧登的守望","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_TimeTravelArena":"在神圣纪元的废弃高塔与帝国纪元的强化巫妖巢穴之间进行时间旅行。\n\n击败鹰首人和帝国军队, 以掌控观察者的遗物, 并改变你的物品的命运。这件遗物允许你交换物品上的力量、智力、敏捷和协调词缀。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_TimeTravelArena_0":"击退遗物附近的鹰首人和帝国军队","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_TimeTravelArena_1":"使用你的时间裂隙技能在不同的纪元中穿梭","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_TimeTravelArena_2":"勇士无论在哪个纪元都是进步的阻碍","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_TimeTravelArena_3":"使用遗物","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_CemeteryPlus":"重织者的墓地","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_CemeteryPlus":"一处被抹灭者的墓地, 击杀初生编织后, 就可以在这里用编织秘境交换其他秘境。","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_GigaTomb":"迷失者的墓穴","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_GigaTomb":"深入庞大的被抹灭者的陵墓, 击败命运编织者, 获取所有周围秘境中的特定奖励。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_GigaTomb_0":"找到并击杀命运编织者","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_GigaTomb_1":"领取墓穴奖励","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_UberTomb":"世界纪念碑","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_UberTomb":"深入错综复杂的被抹灭者的陵墓, 击败飞升初生编织, 从而将新的被抹灭者的陵墓织入所有周围秘境之中。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_UberTomb_0":"找到并击杀飞升初生编织","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_HarbingerEcho":"崩塌视界","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_HarbingerEcho":"与一位已击败此时间线首领的先驱者进行战斗, 并夺取它的战利品。\n\n它掉落的物品与你在击败时间线首领后掉落的物品相同。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerEcho_0":"检查崩塌视界","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerEcho_1":"击杀先驱者","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_HarbingerBossRush":"消逝边缘","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_HarbingerBossRush":"前往黑洞的边缘, 抵达奥罗比斯抹除的所有时间线的尽头。在那里直面一系列曾击败对应时间线首领的先驱者, 并夺回它们所窃取的宝藏。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_0":"检查崩塌视界","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_1":"击杀全部10名先驱者","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_2":"击杀全部10名先驱者（1/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_3":"击杀全部10名先驱者（2/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_4":"击杀全部10名先驱者（3/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_5":"击杀全部10名先驱者（4/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_6":"击杀全部10名先驱者（5/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_7":"击杀全部10名先驱者（6/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_8":"击杀全部10名先驱者（7/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_9":"击杀全部10名先驱者（8/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_HarbingerBossRush_10":"击杀全部10名先驱者（9/10）","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_SuperBeacon":"编织者信标","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_SuperBeacon":"为此秘境中的雄伟信标充能, 以揭示附近大范围区域内的秘境。","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_LizardLevel":"藤壶之王的财宝","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_LizardLevel":"在消失之前, 藤壶之王将自己的宝藏藏在了地下深处的一个隐秘金库中。在洞穴中寻找那个失落的宝箱, 并慷慨地释放那些被困在箱子中的过度炙热的蜥蜴。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_LizardLevel_0":"找到藤壶之王的财宝","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_LizardLevel_1":"打开所有宝箱, 释放全部10只蜥蜴","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_LizardLevel_2":"打开所有宝箱, 释放全部10只蜥蜴（1/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_LizardLevel_3":"打开所有宝箱, 释放全部10只蜥蜴（2/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_LizardLevel_4":"打开所有宝箱, 释放全部10只蜥蜴（3/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_LizardLevel_5":"打开所有宝箱, 释放全部10只蜥蜴（4/10）","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_LizardLevel_6":"打开所有宝箱, 释放全部10只蜥蜴（5/10）",