astSpreader_0":"寻找并保护西部裂隙异兽巢穴","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_TimebeastSpreader_1":"寻找并保护中部裂隙异兽巢穴","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_TimebeastSpreader_2":"寻找并保护北部裂隙异兽巢穴","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_TimebeastSpreader_3":"寻找并保护东部裂隙异兽巢穴","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_TimebeastUltimate":"狂暴海岸","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_TimebeastUltimate":"击杀一只拥有结晶之心且狂暴进化的裂隙异兽, 以解锁将你自己的裂隙异兽血脉进化至超越正常限制的能力。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_TimebeastUltimate_0":"击杀裂隙异兽","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_OmensVeil":"预兆面纱","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_OmensVeil":"清理预兆面纱","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_OmensVeil_0":"清理预兆面纱","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_OmensVeil_1":"一次完成5个预兆事件","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_SuperShadePinnacle":"破碎监牢","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_SuperShadePinnacle":"观察者的幻象开始凝聚成形。必须阻止那些预兆。","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_SuperShadePinnacle_0":"击败预兆与观察者的幻象","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_TimeBeastLedge":"原始倾泻","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_TimeBeastLedge":"在远古峡谷中找到裂隙并击杀其中的裂隙异兽。","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Name_OmenWindowChampions":"混沌之巅.","Monolith_Timelines.Woven_Echo_Description_OmenWindowChampions":"勇士、勇士和更多的勇士, 祝你好运","MonolithObjectives.Monolith_Objective_Woven_Echo_OmenWindowChampions_0":"击败预兆及其勇士","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_0_Affix_A":"虚空抗性穿透","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_1_Affix_A":"护甲","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_2_Affix_A":"近战攻击速度","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_3_Affix_A":"格挡几率","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_4_Affix_A":"施法速度","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_5_Affix_A":"暴击几率","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_6_Affix_A":"暴击伤害加成","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_7_Affix_A":"虚空抗性","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_8_Affix_A":"躲避值","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_9_Affix_A":"元素伤害","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_10_Affix_A":"腐化抗性","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_11_Affix_A":"冻结率加成","Item_Affixes.ItemAffix_12_Affix_A":"火焰伤害","Item_Affixes.ItemAffi